      "body": "## Summary\n\nUpdates all GitHub Actions in the CI workflow files to their latest stable versions.\n\n## Changes\n\n| Action | Previous Version | Updated Version | Files |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `actions/checkout` | v2, v3 | **v6** | ghpages.yml, archive.yml, publish.yml, update.yml |\n| `actions/cache` | v3 | **v5** | ghpages.yml, publish.yml |\n| `actions/upload-artifact` | v4 | **v7** | ghpages.yml, archive.yml, publish.yml |\n| `martinthomson/i-d-template` | v1 | v1 *(no update needed \u2014 only version available)* | \u2014 |\n\n## Notes\n\n- No breaking changes expected for the existing workflow configurations\n- All updated actions have been checked against the GitHub Advisory Database with no known vulnerabilities\n- `actions/checkout@v6` includes improved credential security\n- `actions/cache@v5` uses the new cache backend service (v2 APIs)\n- `actions/upload-artifact@v7` adds support for direct uploads and ESM; existing `path`-based usage is fully compatible",
